Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千八声 啼至血吐 杜鹃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那种小鸟即便流着血也会继续歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的朋友也一直在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边流血一边歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不能再见了 我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的朋友在战场上一直歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的Live可是未来约我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛冈的奶奶受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说现在开车去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这里不熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说等不及呢 还是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不习惯开演前的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是想快点大搞一场的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也无法随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说翼你在紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井女士也说今天很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦十郎老大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们也许知道的 今天是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天Live的结果是赌上了人类的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙关照 我是樱井了子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台上就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 难题就交给老大和了子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就大干一场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太认真了 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绷太紧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后很容易断的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的拍档是翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼摆出这样的表情的话 连我也高兴不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不高兴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来Live的大家也不会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏一起的话总感觉会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你集齐双翼的ZweiWing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多远都能飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何事都能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心扑通直跳 视线无法转移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Live啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phonic Gain显示了预料之内的延长率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全设施支撑不了上升的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去圣遗物会启动 不 是暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noise来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Noise
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死 我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里拥有长枪和剑的就只有我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官还什么都没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,500)}{\3c&H192ABF&}Croitzal ronzell gungnir zizzl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子君 了子君 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青铜蛇之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx70\fscy70\pos(310,312)}Nehushtan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时限式就到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我睁开眼 不要放弃活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想着哪天有机会能唱歌唱到身心疲惫为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有这么多家伙来听我们唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不会吝啬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝唱
